**Upgrade to itws 1.1: System Administrators**

Update the database
====================

Fix the root format
-------------------

Before running icms-update script, you have to fix the root format.

Note: The is not required if you update the database with itws > 1.1 (e.g 1.1.1)

::

  $ cd MY_INSTANCE/database
  $ sed -i -e 's/format="itws"/format="iKaaro"/g' .metadata
  $ git add .metadata && git commit -m 'Fix root format'


Update the database
-------------------

As usual instances must be updated following the standard procedure:

  1. Make a backup

  2. Update the database:

     $ icms-update.py xxx

  3. Rebuild the catalog:

     $ icms-update-catalog.py xxx
